---
title: Pork & Red Wine Lasagne with Fresh Pasta, Homemade Bechamel & Rocket Salad
description: A homemade lasagne is always a treat, you can taste the love that goes into it! This one is packed full of flavourful pork mince in a rich red wine-based ragu. All held together with sheets of delicate pasta and an ooey gooey cheesy bechamel, this dish is sure to be a hit.
